<br>
/pet health report doesnt show fractions, i think anything behind the comma is simply dropped.<br>
So anything from 8.0% - 8.999% will all show up as 8%...<br>
<br>
If i am not mistaken, the summoned 20 hp bracer and ring have a higher rec lvl tag than the ear, so maybe the pet got only 1 hp from each bracer or ring...<br>
<br>
Lets assume the pet had 89 hps, and you nuked it for 81 pts:<br>
8 / 0.89 = 8.988....     8%<br>
<br>
With earring (2hp):<br>
10 / 0.91 = 10.989.... 10%<br>
<br>
With 2 earrings(4hp):<br>
12 / 0.93 = 12.903.... 12%<br>
<br>
With one bracer(1 hp):<br>
9 / 0.9 = 10              10%<br>
<br>
With 2 bracers (2 hp):<br>
10 / 0.91 = 10.989.... 10%<br>
<br>
Try giving the pet an earring and a bracer (3 hps total):<br>
11 / 0.92 = 11.956...  11%<br>
<br>
That should prove if pets equip only 1 or 2 rings / bracers <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=laidee7>laidee7</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 60<br> <font color=#333333>(12/31/02 7:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=918.topic&index=28>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Pet FACTS - SOE/VI Please Acknowledge. </span><hr size=1> Well, Nikatjef seems to know me, and even though I can't place the name, or pull up a face, I have to side with him on the pet buffing during a duel. It is not possible to cast at least your own buffs on a pet while in a duel. As for other buffs, while I've never noticed if STA has an effect, every other buff my pet has ever recieved at any level has always seemed to have an effect. Cleric, shaman, druid (although not to many druid buffs for a darky on TZ, heh), whatever. ALWAYS noticed a difference...<br>
