Quick point -- stamina seems to effect the number of hitpoints you get per level, or at least I've always assumed that it did.  Under this idea, low level pets would have far less benefit from sta buffs than high level pets.  Something like 3sta might not be enough to see a full hitpoint of improvement.  I'd like to see no effect from a high-level shammie sta buff and avatar before agreeing that sta most likely has no effect on pets.<br>
